# ADDENDUM: transport reworked to the agents OTel endpoint (2026-06-10)

User directive: ADK runs must log to the AGENTS OTel endpoint
(/agents/otel/v1/traces) so they appear in the Weave Agents view — the
original calls transport (saveCallStart/End) only fed the Traces page. The
stack was rebuilt in place (same branch names/positions) with the plugin
emitting GenAI-semconv OTel spans through getWeaveTracer (shared provider,
src/genai/provider.ts) — same pipeline as piCodingAgent and the
openai-agents WeaveOtelTracingProcessor, same conventions as the Python
google_adk integration (weave/integrations/google_adk: extractors mirrored
incl. ADK_CAPTURE_MESSAGE_CONTENT_IN_SPANS gate, GOOGLE_GENAI_USE_VERTEXAI
provider naming, parts-model messages, tool definitions). Calls-era
versions of these slices: 91e4f038ee^..4fde323b1c history (notes on
c059413134 / ac1e328342 / d1cab0e03e / 4fde323b1c).

Key mechanics: spans parented via otelTrace.setSpan contexts; plugin
beforeExit hook registers BEFORE the provider's (listeners fire in
registration order — dangling spans must end before the provider flush);
tests inject InMemorySpanExporter via settings.genai.spanProcessor +
clearWeaveTracerProvider between tests; semconv.ts gained
gen_ai.agent.description/id + gen_ai.tool.definitions.

